  52:../../libs/libDaisy/src/per/dac.h ****     /** Sets the number of bits per sample transmitted out of the DAC.
  53:../../libs/libDaisy/src/per/dac.h ****      ** The output range will be: 0V - VDDA
  54:../../libs/libDaisy/src/per/dac.h ****      ** The resolution will be roughly: bitdepth / (VDDA - 0V) 
